[new][dlmodule] modification for dlmodule.

[Description in detail]
1. add APIs: app_open (dlopen *_res.so and *.so) & app_close (close
   module).

   defined.

4. add log to debug module issues.

6. fixed ua.py compiler error.

author: Xiaoming Xi
message:
[bug][build] Fix build error if both RT_USING_PTHREADS and RT_USING_LIBC are enabled

ext-redmine: #7184, REDMINE-7184

[Description in detail]
If _GNU_SOURCE is defined, all GNU extensions are enabled including pthread feature, which is conflicted with RT-Thread implementation.
According to rt-thread lts v3.1, POSIX version up to POSIX.1b-1993 is enabled, which means pthread is disabled in standard lib.

Change-Id: I934e93723fb0bef5a29dc177cef59ba4a195ff5c
